<div class="topImage"><a href="http://www.ilo.org/dyn/media/mediasearch.fiche?p_lang=en&p_ref=e3897" onclick="newWin('http://www.ilo.org/dyn/media/mediasearch.fiche?p_lang=en&p_ref=e3897'); return false;" class="none"><img src="http://www.ilo.org/dyn/media/images/thumbs/e3897.jpg" border="0" alt="Select to magnify the image"></a>
